# Job Components

This folder will contain React components related to job management for the user.

## Suggested Components

- **JobList.tsx**: List of all jobs for the current user.
- **JobForm.tsx**: Form for creating or editing a job entry.
- **JobView.tsx**: View details of a single job.
- **JobCard.tsx**: Card component for displaying job summary.

## Description

- Use Tailwind CSS for styling.
- Integrate with backend API for CRUD operations on jobs.
- Allow users to add, edit, view, and delete job postings.

